Salary Administration Assistant - PT Europe Marine Control Indonesia
Salary Administration Assistant  -
Salary Administration Assistant
Responsibilities
As a Salary Administration Assistant you will be in charge of the whole salary administration for our clients. You will have tasks like issuing timesheets, doing the salary calculation and issuing salary specifications. Requirements:-       Basic education in accounting, finance & administration and/or track record on such level;-       Finance & administration and/or salary administration experience-       Strong coordination and planning skills, being able to handle multi tasks at the same time;-       Strong in keeping structure and handle effective and adequately;-       Advanced English language skills, both oral and written;-       Advanced computer skills, in all relevant MS office and administration applications.
